OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fstranded abroad as school  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ben, 17, was due home on Saturday in   
OL,6, plenty of time to take his maths GCSE  
OL,7, on Tuesday, but after a cancelled      
OL,8, flight and a frantic scrabble for train
OL,9, tickets, he will only just make it.    
OL,11,FHe is one of thousands of British      
OL,12,Fholiday-makers thought to be stranded  
OL,13,Fabroad, after the cancellation of more 
OL,14,Fthan 100 flights over the weekend.     
OL,16,FAmong them are hundreds of school      
OL,17,Fpupils and some teachers set to miss   
OL,18,Fschool on Monday after half-term.      
OL,20,FAnd they face an anxious journey home. 
